send it to a couple of buddies. Then insinuate that if they don't sign 
up for their own copy, you'll make 'em sit through all your holiday 
pictures. To avoid this fate, they'll need to go to:  
http://www.pcworld.com/resource/newsletters/index.asp?sub_source=NL_XB  

